</strong></p><p> The band <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scissor-sisters-interview-reunion-tour-jake-shears-ana-matronic-susan-boyle-homophobia-new-album-3810544">spoke to <em>NME</em> in November</a> about their reunion tour. “I could be completely wrong about this, but it did feel like there was sort of a zeitgeist moment where [interest in the band] was bubbling up a little bit,” said Babydaddy. “It just felt like there was enough distance for us. I don&#39;t think five years ago we were quite ready to start reminiscing about those days.”</p><p> They were also asked if being labelled a &#39;gay band&#39; was grating for them.</p><p> “It did, yeah. I was looking at our straight counterparts, and, like, I had a bit of resentment that we sort of had this extra label that made it easier for some [people] to dismiss us. And I think I had a bit of a chip on my shoulder about that,” said Shears.</p><p> Babydaddy added: “It&#39;s a lot less loaded now, but in that moment, I think there was a question of, like, &#39;Are people saying that to put [the band] in its own little box?&#39; I don&#39;t really know what it was supposed to say, except that we were open about who we were, and there were some themes [in our music] that were definitely queer themes.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scissor-sisters-announce-intimate-warm-up-shows-ahead-of-uk-and-ireland-arena-tour-3849403">Scissor Sisters announce intimate warm-up shows ahead of UK and Ireland arena tour</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）在超级英雄电影中“失去了兴趣”，他说扮演蝙蝠侠正在“令人生畏” https://www.nme.com/news/film/ben-affleck-has-lost-interest-interest-in-superhero-movies-says-say-playing-batman-was-was-crciating-3849390？ m_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = ben-affleck-has-lost-interest-superhero-movies-says-says-says-says-says-play-batman-was-was-crocruciatingVictoria Luxford Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:10:57 +0000 Film NewsNewsUncategorisedBatmanDC Extended Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3849390 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我每天上班的东西非常不满”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ben-affleck-has-lost-interest-in-superhero-movies-says-playing-batman-was-excruciating-3849390">本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）对超级英雄电影的“失去了兴趣”，他说《蝙蝠侠》（Batman）“令人难以置信”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ben-Affleck-Batman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ben-affleck">本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）</a>公开了他对扮演<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/batman">蝙蝠侠</a>不喜欢的东西，以及为什么他不再从事超级英雄类型的工作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/zack-snyders-justice-league-review-2901050">扎克·斯奈德（Zack Snyder）的正义联盟评论：坚定的更新粉丝可以为此感到自豪</a></li></ul><p>奥斯卡奖得主被当作《黑暗骑士》（Dark Knight），作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/dc-extended-universe">DC扩展宇宙</a>在2016年至2023年之间的一部分，出现在<em>Batman v Superman：正义</em>，<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/suicide-squad">自杀小队</a>，正义联盟</em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-flash"><em>Flash</em>中。</a>计划着一部为他的角色的电影，但最终取消了2022年由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-pattinson">罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）</a>主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-batman"><em>蝙蝠侠</em></a>。</p><p> Affleck在接受<a href="https://www.gq.com/story/inside-ben-afflecks-plan-to-remake-hollywood?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dhtwitter&amp;utm_content=null" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>GQ</em></a>讲话时回顾了自己的角色，并扩大了他以前不喜欢玩他的声明。他说：“有很多原因为什么这是一次非常令人发指的经历。” “而且它们并不是与超级英雄电影或其他任何事情的简单动态有关。我对再次下降这种特定的流派不感兴趣，不是因为那种糟糕的经历，而只是：我对这部电影的感兴趣失去了兴趣”。</p><p>他继续说：“我当然不想复制这样的经历。其中很多是对议程，理解，期望的未对准。而且，顺便说一句，我当时也没有为当时的方程式带来任何特别的奇妙之处。我也有自己的失败，重大的失败，在那个过程和当时和当时和当时和当时。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="扎克·斯奈德（Zack Snyder）的正义联盟 - 官方预告片 - 华纳兄弟英国" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ui37YKQ9AC4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>演员后来说他的消极记忆的原因部分是个人的。他说：“就为什么我有糟糕的经历而言，部分原因是我每天上班的东西非常不满。” “我没有引起问题，但是我进来了，我做了工作，然后回家了。但是你必须做的比这要好一些。”</p><p>在讨论由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gunn">詹姆斯·冈恩（James Gunn）</a>重新启动的共享宇宙出了什么问题时，阿弗莱克（Affleck）说，他觉得角色变得太成年了。他解释说：“发生的事情是，它开始对大部分观众来说太老了。” “就像当时我自己的儿子一样，也太害怕看电影了。所以当我看到自己当时想，&#39;哦，该死，我们有问题&#39;”。</p><p>最近，宣布本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）的一部旧电影《喜剧<em>教条》</em> （Comedy Dogma）正在制作中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dogma-2-is-in-the-works-matt-damon-and-ben-affleck-expected-to-return-3813560">明星和最好的朋友马特·达蒙（Matt Damon）预计会返回</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ben-affleck-has-lost-interest-in-superhero-movies-says-playing-batman-was-excruciating-3849390">本·阿弗莱克（Ben Affleck）对超级英雄电影的“失去了兴趣”，他说《蝙蝠侠》（Batman）“令人难以置信”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
